  "texts": [
    "The stages of ChatGPT usage include designing projects, decomposing problems, acquiring unfamiliar knowledge, coding, and debugging.",
    "The advantages of using ChatGPT include having extensive programming knowledge, contextualized and varied responses, and accurate and efficient feedback.",
    "Other studies have also advocated for the advantages of ChatGPT, such as providing rapid and accurate responses, availability at any time and location, ease of access, utilizing natural language, facilitating personalized learning, supporting multiple languages, offering clear explanations and programming examples, as well as providing resources for advanced topics.",
    "Besides, the study identified several disadvantages of using ChatGPT, including inaccurate codes, limited input and output, and technical problems.",
    "Other studies have also identified additional disadvantages, such as causing occupational anxiety, providing inadequate information, lacking a real programming environment, and potentially increasing laziness among programmers (Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023a)."
